    "We restricted this analysis to two models (gpt-4 and gpt-3.5-turbo) and three ontologies (CL with 2121 issues, UBERON with 2300 issues, and ENVO with 1436 issues indexed).Including the GitHub issues improved performance of all models, although performance was still beneath manually authored definitions (Table 7).",
